-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Tank Multiple Roots Configuration
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

This configuration shows an example where the Toolkit code and configuration
resides in one location on disk and the actual data resides in another.

Before this configuration can be auto-installed, it needs to be
adjusted to match the disk location where you want to have the code
and the data for your setup.

For more information, go to the following url: 
https://support.shotgunsoftware.com/entries/95442768

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
